              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-green-600">72.3%</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-green-600">127%</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold">あり</span></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">南関4場＋中央全場</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">AI分析型。買い切りプランで永久利用可</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-500">🥈 2位</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">nankan-analytics</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">68.1%</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">115%</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold">あり</span></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">南関4場特化</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3">南関データ量No.1。穴馬発見に強い</td>
